<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>personal note to seoman</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Perin">Perin</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 8:55 a.m. 20/2/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> personal note to seoman<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1059" TARGET=_self>Halfling Banditos</A> (Seoman Snowlock[CC-Council])
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Seoman hail brother..although i question whether i should call you that. Last night you accused me of many things. Looting your corpse after dying while link dead, curseing at other players, killing newbies, camping corpses to kill ppl over and over...etc etc...

<BR>After i tryed to tell you that you were mistaken you told me MANY people on THIS board have posted compaining about ME. Well im sorry but i must have missed those "posts". Because all i see is this one vauge post about halflings and humans not being nice... :/
<BR>I must admit i'm confused still brother. At no time in the past have I EVER....
<P>1) Killed a newbie.
<P>2) Killed anyone of my own race that did not attack me or a friend of mine first.
<P>3) Looted a corpse of one that is of my race, unless said corpse belonged to a friend or enemy.
<P>4) Cursed at ANYONE in game without it being in a Role Playing text.
<P>5) Pked in general unless it was an evil race and or enemy of mine and/or a friend of mine.
<P>6) Camped a corpse in any way, shape or form. I always let them retrieve there possesions that are left and then leave in peace, if thats what they choose. If they sick around and/or pester me yes i will attack them again.
<P>If you have any questions and or doubts about the above statements please talk to those in game that i have fought. A few names that come to mind are Vampton, Vilar, Stonemann, Skandar(sp?), a few trolls that i forget there names, and quite a few more dark elfs that remeber me better then i remember them no doubt...ohh and next time please confirm your stories you hear before blindly attacking a brother...
<P>A Lost Brother,
<P>Perin, Halfling Druid, Dark Race Slayer Extrodinare
<P>&gt; Who were the halflings that camped your corpse? I'd be
<BR>&gt; interested to know considering I lead most of the raids by the
<BR>&gt; halflings into Dark Elven Territory and any Dark Elves we've
<BR>&gt; killed will tell you we not only never camp corpses, we don't
<BR>&gt; kill named daries either who have died elsewhere. I WOULD like
<BR>&gt; to know which halflings were doing so though. This is the kind
<BR>&gt; of bullshit that makes fighting each other less fun and more
<BR>&gt; frustrating and I'd prefer to think we have higher quality
<BR>&gt; players on our beloved PvP server than this. Either way...if you
<BR>&gt; see me...run :)
<P>&gt; Seo, ignoring Gray Rages pitiful attempts at getting a little
<BR>&gt; attention for his newbie guild below ;)
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
